Package: DataCraftR
Type: Package
Title: Create Data Sets Interactively
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Carlos", "Rivera",
      email = "caariveramo@unal.edu.co",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Shiny-based addins to create datasets interactively through graphical 
    interfaces. Users can adjust plot elements to set parameters for data 
    generation, and the resulting datasets are returned to the R environment 
    for analysis or visualization.
